<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَمَنْ بَلَغَ رَشِيداً <span class="c2">(١)</span>،<span class="c5"> أَوْ مَجْنُوناً ثُمَّ عَقَلَ وَرَشَدَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- انْفَكَّ الحَجْرُ عَنْهُ بِلَا حُكْمٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَأُعْطِيَ مَالَهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- لَا قَبْلَ ذَلِكَ بِحَالٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَبُلُوغُ ذَكَرٍ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> بِإِمْنَاءٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> أَوْ تَمَامِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> خَمْسَ عَشْرَةَ سَنَةً.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> أَوْ نَبَاتِ شَعْرٍ خَشِنٍ حَوْلَ قُبُلِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأُنْثَى:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> <span class="c4">[٢]</span> <span class="c4">[٣]</span> بِذَلِكَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَبِحَيْضٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَحَمْلُهَا دَلِيلُ إِمْنَاءٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَلَا يُدْفَعُ إِلَيْهِ مَالُهُ حَتَّى يُخْتَبَرَ بِمَا يَلِيقُ بِهِ، وَيُؤْنَسَ رُشْدُهُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَمَحَلُّهُ قَبْلَ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> بُلُوغٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (ب): عبداً.<br>(٢) في (ب): وإتمام.<br>(٣) قبل سقطت من (ب).</p> </div>